tipContent: Sawirro tayo sare leh waxay ka caawiyaan martida inay si fiican u fahmaan hantiyeedkaaga waxayna kordhiyaan diiwaangelinta. Isticmaal iftiin dabiici ah oo muuji astaamaha ugu fiican.
tips: Isticmaal iftiin dabiici ah marka ay suurtagal tahay
Ku dar meelaha kala duwan ee booskaaga
Ka dhig sawirrada kuwo cusub oo sax ah
